          }
        },
        {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is it good for travel and naps?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes — it's one of the best travel companions you can pack. Lightweight, compact, and effective in any lighting environment. Works just as well on a plane, train, or couch.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "faq_item",
